							<h4>the client</h4>
							<p>This concept project was completed during my User Experience Design Immersive course at General Assembly (December 2014)</p>
							<h4>the timeline</h4>
							<p>2 weeks</p>
							<h4>the team</h4>
							<p>Arielle Cook</p>
