			<section id="#prototype-development" class="row last-section">
				<div class="sub-section-heading">prototype development</div>
				<div class="row sub-section bg-white">
					<div class="container">
						<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-8">
							<h2>sketching, wireframing,&nbsp;</h2>
							<div class="h2-wrap">
								<div class="h2-helper">low-fi prototyping and testing</div>
							</div>
							<p>Armed with the sitemap and user flows, I started sketching some initial concepts. These were iteratively refined and turned into a low-fi interactive prototype using Illustrator and Invision.</p>
							<p>This prototype was then tested with 8 people who would match the target audience of the site.</p>
